# Design System

Use NeoGlass UI.

Dark mode first.

Inspired by

- Linear
- TradingView
- Apple VisionOS
- Arc Browser
- Vercel Dashboard

Use

- Glassmorphism
- Soft Neomorphic Shadows
- Floating Panels

Never use classic neumorphism.

Cards

- rounded-3xl
- backdrop-blur-2xl
- border-white/10

Buttons

- rounded-xl

Inputs

- glass style

Use Geist font.

Animations

Framer Motion

200-300ms

Always prioritize readability.